text:
Crayon Spectacles AG
Jason Statham Str. 2
60312 Oslo
London
12. July 2023
Advance Payment Guarantee No. 101BGI2347101
Dear Sirs,
We have been informed that a contract, hereinafter "Underlying Contract", has been
concluded between you and Day Light Vison AG, Kitt Str. 4, 20149 Hamburg, Germany
hereinafter "Principal", on 01.06.2023 under ref. No. 156523211 for the delivery of Anti Glare
Lenses at a total price of EUR 82.000,00 and that the Underlying Contract stipulates that an
advance payment in the amount of 20% of the total price be effected against an Advance
Payment Guarantee
This being premised, we, Goods Bank, Frankfurt, hereby irrevocably undertake to pay you
without delay on your first written demand for payment an amount up to
EUR 82.000,00
(in words: Euro Eighty Two thousand)
provided your demand for payment is simultaneously supported by your written statement
(whether in the demand itself or in a separate document(s) accompanying the demand and
referred to in it) stating
a) that the Principal is in breach of his obligation(s) under the Underlying Contract, and
b) the respect in which the Principal is in breach, and
c) that the obligation(s) in respect of which the Principal is in breach is/are covered by
the present guarantee and that you are therefore entitled to demand repayment of
the advance payment up to the amount of the demand for payment.
This guarantee shall remain valid and in full force and effect up to 23.12.2024, provided
that it is a condition of this guarantee that, in the event you give The Guarantor on or prior
to the said expiry date of this guarantee (or any subsequent extension of that expiry Date
In accordance with this provision) signed written notification requesting an extension the
Guarantor will (a) automatically extend this guarantee for such period (not exceeding 365
days) from that expiry date or extension as you may specify in that notification or (b)
pay the amount of the guarantee.
This guarantee shall enter into effect if and to the extent the advance payment of EUR
12.000,00 is credited in full without reserve to Principal's account no. 100 546520 held with
us in Frankfurt, IBAN DE12 5653 6534 6662 1900 00 with reference to this guarantee, at his
free disposal.
This guarantee shall expire, even if this document is not returned, on 24. December 2024,
and shall then be null and void, if and to the extent that no demand under this guarantee in
accordance with its conditions has reached us in Frankfurt by the end of that day.
This guarantee is transferable with our written consent only.
This guarantee is subject to URDG and the laws of Ireland.
Goods Bank
